  p.p We integrate with the tools you're already using, like GitHub and Slack, to automatically deploy commits and launch containers in your Sandbox when you create branches and notify you when they are updated via Slack. It's easy to share Sandboxes in a team as you develop and test your applicationâ€”and you can continue to use your existing tools and processes for deployment without having to change the way you work.
